##In Wuhan, life goes on

Micro Signal Zhenshigushi1

Function description, every day a moving original true story.

In the New Year of 2020, COVID-19 pneumonia broke out in Wuhan, and as the epidemic spread, most residents of Wuhan and Hubei chose to prevent the disease at home. City services such as health care workers, delivery boys to stay at their posts, residents of the epidemic area to make delicious food, together to Brush Douyin, watching "lost mother" to combat epidemic anxiety. We're seeing people's lives go on in the cold.

Yu Qiang, Wuhan Hanyang District Financial Practitioner

My daughter, who was born in a designated hospital, is my greatest joy
My family lives not far from the south China Seafood Wholesale Market, one of the places where the outbreak began. The First Hospital in Wuhan, where my wife gave birth, is also the closest third-class hospital to the south China market.
January 17, his wife abdominal pain, we rushed to the hospital, then the hospital wearing masks were not many people, the mood in Wuhan is also relatively optimistic. The next day, the wife gave birth to a daughter, and we stayed another three days, leaving on the 21st. Later I learned that during childbirth, Wuhan First Hospital on the 18th and 21st, respectively, new pneumonia patients died. It was particularly noticeable that, on the day academician Zhong Nanshan spoke, almost everyone in the hospital was wearing face masks.
When I got home, the infection had been weighing on me. Years ago the last two days, I am ready to return to work unit, the leadership understand my situation, fear of infection, persuade me to take good care of my wife and daughter at home isolation. Considering the situation, my brother and I were lucky enough to buy enough meat and eggs and vegetables to feed our family for more than half a month on the day before the lockdown. Before the city closed more than 10 hours, my brother and father drove back to Jiangxi home, home isolation.
Now, my wife and daughter are in excellent health, I am busy at home, looking at the pedometer software, colleagues and friends are only a poor 100 steps 200 steps, I actually have more than 7,000 steps high. Busy to give her name, make her laugh, my heart is really great satisfaction, not busy, I brush a shih tone, see the "Orong mother" , enrich the time.
I felt very lucky, a blessed stroke of luck. These days, I suddenly understand that people are obsessed with drying the baby, the child is really lovely, now in the atmosphere, in the circle of friends drying the baby is not suitable, I specifically downloaded Douyin, in the above video recording the growth of my daughter bit by bit.

Liang Tian Wuhan Wuchang District Company Finance
2,000 miles away, pretending to sit in a movie theater together

After the news of the Wuhan Lockdown was released, my boyfriend seemed more nervous than I was, and every once in a while he would send me a message on Wechat to check up on me and make sure I didn't go out and have a fever.
We met and fell in love when we were college students in Wuhan. After graduation, I was in Wuhan. He was in Harbin, more than 2,000 kilometers away, and the relationship was still very good. It was supposed to be good to meet my parents in Wuhan after the Spring Festival and make wedding plans. However, after the outbreak of the epidemic, i'M GONNA have to cancel.
As the news about Wuhan increased, the boyfriend more and more do not trust, although I repeatedly stressed that the home supplies are adequate, in good condition, but he did not understand the real situation here, or anxious around.
I was upset at first. I was home quarantined, not arrested. There's no need to worry. Later, he realized that he could not tell the truth from the outside world, and could not help but be worried.
To help him relax, I kept sending him screenshots of my jokes on Weibo, hoping to ease the tension between us. I've just counted twenty-eight screenshots I've sent him over the past few days, and although the epidemic is still very much under threat, it's probably best to stay positive if we're going to get through it together.
On New Year's Eve, it was strangely quiet outside. I stayed in the cabin and chatted with my boyfriend on video, we all envy those couples who can spend New Year's Eve together, set off fireworks and go to the cinema to see the New Year's Eve.
Speaking of which, he suddenly suggested that we turn on our computers together, play the movie lost in China with a watermelon video, and pretend we were sitting in a movie theater.
So we spent a special New Year together, connected by the Internet.

Wu Yi, delivery man, Hongshan district, Wuhan City
During the outbreak, I sent my wife's cooking to the doctor
After the city was shut down, my colleagues and I continued to deliver the tickets. The road is deserted, except for the people out shopping, the street can see most of the sanitation workers, take-out and delivery boy. The last few days of delivery, I also experienced a lot of warm story.

On January 26, just before work was over, I received an order, with a note that read, "mom's cooking, send it to Dad, my dad's a front-line doctor, thank you. ".
I went to pick up the package at an address, and a woman answered the door. She was very polite and kept thanking me. Then he gave me a tote bag, which contained the wrapped cutlery and a lunch box. I dropped off the treat at a hotel in Florida, about 2 km from their home.
The hotel is closer to Wuchang Hospital, where I suspect the paramedics are staying after work instead of going home. It says to take the food to room 801. I dropped it off at 801, and the guy who answered said he wasn't Dr. Chen, who lives in the next room. Something happened at the hospital. He just went back.
I wonder when he'll be able to eat his wife's cooking that day.
Shortly after 8 pm on January 27, my electric car broke down due to lack of electricity. After changing the battery, I was smoking by the side of the road. I heard a young lady behind me shouting: "GO WUHAN! " I suddenly felt smoke in my eyes.
Orders are not many days, I came home from work early in the evening to eat, call my mother to report safe, can go to bed early feel very satisfied. I'm not from Wuhan. I went to university here for four years. Many relatives and friends are here. I also met many warm Wuhan People. Haven't you seen Mose from Wuhan? I believe that everything will be fine in Wuhan.

Sales in Qingshan District, Wuhan, Wuhan
Sealing the city for seven days, on-line to see the new year file to bring us a ray of comfort
Both friends'wives are still being treated for pneumonia. In the community, the security guard "don't wander off" was amplified several times by the loudspeaker. I've been out of the city twice in seven days, once to buy groceries, another time to buy snacks for my daughter, and have to hesitate for half a day when I push the elevator when I go downstairs.
Due to the closure of the city, years ago to prepare in the cinema to see the New Year's Day file wish can not be realized. On the first day of the Lunar New Year, my family stayed up all night to watch "lost mom" online. When I saw mom nagging about her son and his impatient expression in the movie, I thought of my mother and said to my daughter, "your grandma is nagging too. " After all, in fact, I miss my mother in my heart, our neighborhood is only two stops away from our parents'house, but for now, we don't know when the next meeting will be.
The daughter in one side grumbles, "Dad, you also Nag AH. ". My wife and I laughed together, usually because she had to keep an eye on her homework, will inevitably be more severe. After living in fear for so long, I want nothing more than my family to be safe and happy.
The midnight movie brought a little bit of happiness to our family, and I'm grateful to Xu Zheng for that. I expressed my thanks in the comments area, and received the response of strangers constantly "will be safe. ".

Xianning, Hubei Province
Douyin on the anti-epidemic video, hidden mother's love
During the Spring Festival, my parents would have drinks with relatives, talk about the family gossip for a year, and play video games with a group of children after dinner. These scenes formed my whole memory of the new year. And this can not walk around the Spring Festival, destined to be some special.
There were only three of us in the house. We simply ate some New Year's Eve dinner. No one had any topic to break the silence. My parents sat on the couch, occasionally reading a few sentences about the outbreak from an unknown source, sighing repeatedly on their mobile phones, and CCTV New Year's Gala became even more desolate. On second thought, why don't I just get my parents'cell phones and play video games with them. Play a few days, dad more and more obsessed, every day pestering me to play games.
Not Play the game of the mother, these days on the Douyin like more than a thousand videos, but also pulled me to watch. In the past, most of the videos my mother watched were about the matching of makeup and the Movement of Stars. She loved beauty and always kept a girlish heart. She always said that she would go out and take some photos as good as the video when she had time.
Yesterday, I clicked on her douyin interface and found that my mother, who has always paid little attention to the news and current affairs, had recently become all kinds of popular science videos. Instead of reading random articles, she calmed down a lot, but began to teach me not to panic.
Now, watching my parents escape from the oppressive atmosphere, I feel more or less reassured.

Staff of the Wuhan Kong Hon District Office
For half a month in isolation, I relied on my mom's cooking to combat my anxiety
Shortly after New Year's Day, there was a suspected case in my unit. After the doctors determined that it was mostly pneumonia, I returned home to quarantine. At that time, my parents didn't care too much. Before Academician Zhong Nanshan came out to speak, they didn't listen to my advice and walked to the Hankou Railway Station to pick up relatives and friends.
On the day of the city closure in Wuhan, my family went to the supermarket to buy vegetables. My mother said there was a lot of pork in the house. After cleaning up only to find that pork only less than a catty, but a lot of hoarding of chicken, beef and mutton. Quarantine, the whole family are staying together, this time is very rare, every day to eat sleep to eat, play games to see the news, to see the construction of Vulcan Mountain Hospital. To my special surprise, I found that my mother had many different ways of cooking.
Material is limited, mother every meal is guaranteed to have three dishes, she cut up Chinese cabbage Bangzi pickled, made a spicy dish. Anxiety lowered the sensitivity of my mouth. This dish was so popular with me that I decided to record a short video of my mother's cooking for the sake of her. To this end, my mother also made the kind of restaurant only available in the beef powder, taste good. Apart from eating well, I look at the statistics of my colleagues'health every day, and I am very happy to see that everyone is healthy.
The only problem is, the beef is hard and hard to digest, and I don't move around at home every day, and I have some digestive problems. On January 28th, I decided to take 1,000 steps and hold on to exercise to help digest. In my bedroom and living room, I circled back and forth many times. The next day, I saw that there were only 924 steps.
I've been doing a lot of soul searching, and the house is still too small, so when this epidemic is over, I'M GONNA try.

Liang Tian Wuhan Wuchang District Company Finance
2,000 miles away, pretending to sit in a movie theater together

After the news of the Wuhan Lockdown was released, my boyfriend seemed more nervous than I was, and every once in a while he would send me a message on Wechat to check up on me and make sure I didn't go out and have a fever.
We met and fell in love when we were college students in Wuhan. After graduation, I was in Wuhan. He was in Harbin, more than 2,000 kilometers away, and the relationship was still very good. It was supposed to be good to meet my parents in Wuhan after the Spring Festival and make wedding plans. However, after the outbreak of the epidemic, i'M GONNA have to cancel.
As the news about Wuhan increased, the boyfriend more and more do not trust, although I repeatedly stressed that the home supplies are adequate, in good condition, but he did not understand the real situation here, or anxious around.
I was upset at first. I was home quarantined, not arrested. There's no need to worry. Later, he realized that he could not tell the truth from the outside world, and could not help but be worried.
To help him relax, I kept sending him screenshots of my jokes on Weibo, hoping to ease the tension between us. I've just counted twenty-eight screenshots I've sent him over the past few days, and although the epidemic is still very much under threat, it's probably best to stay positive if we're going to get through it together.
On New Year's Eve, it was strangely quiet outside. I stayed in the cabin and chatted with my boyfriend on video, we all envy those couples who can spend New Year's Eve together, set off fireworks and go to the cinema to see the New Year's Eve.
Speaking of which, he suddenly suggested that we turn on our computers together, play the movie lost in China with a watermelon video, and pretend we were sitting in a movie theater.
So we spent a special New Year together, connected by the Internet.

Staff of the Wuhan Kong Hon District Office
For half a month in isolation, I relied on my mom's cooking to combat my anxiety
Shortly after New Year's Day, there was a suspected case in my unit. After the doctors determined that it was mostly pneumonia, I returned home to quarantine. At that time, my parents didn't care too much. Before Academician Zhong Nanshan came out to speak, they didn't listen to my advice and walked to the Hankou Railway Station to pick up relatives and friends.
On the day of the city closure in Wuhan, my family went to the supermarket to buy vegetables. My mother said there was a lot of pork in the house. After cleaning up only to find that pork only less than a catty, but a lot of hoarding of chicken, beef and mutton. Quarantine, the whole family are staying together, this time is very rare, every day to eat sleep to eat, play games to see the news, to see the construction of Vulcan Mountain Hospital. To my special surprise, I found that my mother had many different ways of cooking.
Material is limited, mother every meal is guaranteed to have three dishes, she cut up Chinese cabbage Bangzi pickled, made a spicy dish. Anxiety lowered the sensitivity of my mouth. This dish was so popular with me that I decided to record a short video of my mother's cooking for the sake of her. To this end, my mother also made the kind of restaurant only available in the beef powder, taste good. Apart from eating well, I look at the statistics of my colleagues'health every day, and I am very happy to see that everyone is healthy.
The only problem is, the beef is hard and hard to digest, and I don't move around at home every day, and I have some digestive problems. On January 28th, I decided to take 1,000 steps and hold on to exercise to help digest. In my bedroom and living room, I circled back and forth many times. The next day, I saw that there were only 924 steps.
I've been doing a lot of soul searching, and the house is still too small, so when this epidemic is over, I'M GONNA try.

North Drift 9 years, a pot of wine, a movie to let the family close
I went to university in Beijing and stayed in Beijing for nine years after graduation. Because I chose to drift north, marriage problems are not smooth, I and parents communication has been stumbling.
Usually and parents get together not much, this year the village does not let New Year, a family stay together, parents unexpectedly very happy. For this, the parents began to try to make delicious food. My father opened a jar of old wine, saying it was five years old. He cheerfully opened the seal and poured the wine from the jar into a glass bottle
After the wine was served, I saw some turbidity in the glass and frowned subconsciously. He busy said nothing nothing nothing for a long time, a little precipitation, perhaps taste better. I picked up my glass and he looked at me nervously.
I drank it, the taste is very weak, I think the seal is not good reason. I say it's good, it's good, it's five years old. He obviously saw my perfunctory, picked it up and took a drink, and realized it didn't taste very good, and said, it's been there a long time, it's no good, you don't have to drink it if you don't like it.
After lunch, he went to saw wood, and I brushed the sound, which happened to be in the movie lost in translation. I saw that the mother and son in the movie had to stay in a confined space for a long time in order to travel to Moscow, and all kinds of intergenerational conflicts gradually broke out, mother and son killed each other all the way.
Looking at the movie smiled for a while, I suddenly remembered the special situation of this year's Spring Festival, and my father has not finished the cup of wine. The original understanding between people really so difficult, even mother and son, father and son, the mind is often difficult to communicate each other. The son in the movie does not understand the mother's control, I also do not understand the father because can not keep up with the pace of life, the innermost feelings worry. I wish my parents could have seen the scene in the movie where mother and Son Open up to each other, and the family can communicate better and understand each other's choices.
At dinner, when I set the table and my brother asked what to drink, I turned to my father and said, why don't you bring me Your five-year-old. Father Leng for a while, all of a sudden smile, said good, good, happy like a little red flower was sent to the children.
These days, my father has been busy at home Trivia, I am still looking for the opportunity to pull him together to see "lost mother" . The rift between our father and son might be unfrozen this winter by a movie like this.

Usually and parents get together not much, this year the village does not let New Year, a family stay together, parents unexpectedly very happy. For this, the parents began to try to make delicious food. My father opened a jar of old wine, saying it was five years old. He cheerfully opened the seal and poured the wine from the jar into a glass bottle
After the wine was served, I saw some turbidity in the glass and frowned subconsciously. He busy said nothing nothing nothing for a long time, a little precipitation, perhaps taste better. I picked up my glass and he looked at me nervously.
I drank it, the taste is very weak, I think the seal is not good reason. I say it's good, it's good, it's five years old. He obviously saw my perfunctory, picked it up and took a drink, and realized it didn't taste very good, and said, it's been there a long time, it's no good, you don't have to drink it if you don't like it.
After lunch, he went to saw wood, and I brushed the sound, which happened to be in the movie lost in translation. I saw that the mother and son in the movie had to stay in a confined space for a long time in order to travel to Moscow, and all kinds of intergenerational conflicts gradually broke out, mother and son killed each other all the way.
Looking at the movie smiled for a while, I suddenly remembered the special situation of this year's Spring Festival, and my father has not finished the cup of wine. The original understanding between people really so difficult, even mother and son, father and son, the mind is often difficult to communicate each other. The son in the movie does not understand the mother's control, I also do not understand the father because can not keep up with the pace of life, the innermost feelings worry. I wish my parents could have seen the scene in the movie where mother and Son Open up to each other, and the family can communicate better and understand each other's choices.
At dinner, when I set the table and my brother asked what to drink, I turned to my father and said, why don't you bring me Your five-year-old. Father Leng for a while, all of a sudden smile, said good, good, happy like a little red flower was sent to the children.
These days, my father has been busy at home Trivia, I am still looking for the opportunity to pull him together to see "lost mother" . The rift between our father and son might be unfrozen this winter by a movie like this.
